members.name: Chris Cox
members.title: Lead Child & Youth Program Coordinator
members.bio: Chris Cox leads the Iowa Army National Guard Child & Youth Program. He grew up in a Guard family and knows firsthand how much encouragement matters. Chris loves building experiences where military-connected youth can be themselves, learn new skills, and feel proud of the role they play at home.
